---
name: Cloudability API Reference
description: Cloudability V3 API endpoints, auth methods, and US base URL for Siemens FinOps integration
type: reference
---
- Base URL: https://api.cloudability.com (US — NOT EU)
- Auth: Basic Auth with API key as username, empty password
- Date params: `start_date` and `end_date` (NOT `start`/`end`)
- Response field: `results` array (NOT `result`)
- Key endpoints: /v3/reporting/cost/run, /v3/rightsizing, /v3/budgets, /v3/anomalies
- Environment ID: f2ee502f-2f35-45c1-8bc5-7d4748f637b6 (for UI reference only, not used in API)
